title: A Car Is Reborn (Jaguar Series I E-Type 4.2 restoration project)
description:
Mark Evans restores perhaps the classiest of classic cars, a 1965 series 1.1 E-Type Jaguar, from farmers field to concourse condition.

A comprehensive and instructional series, 'A Car Is Reborn' forms the definitive guide to restoring a classic car. Each programme deals with a different aspect of the restoration process with appropriate help and advice on procedure and safety from relevant experts. Every aspect of classic car restoration is touched on from metalwork restoration to leather upholstery.
